===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|lang=fro|desgouster||to put off one's appetite}}, from {{term|lang=fro|des-||dis-}} + {{term|lang=fro|gouster}}, {{term|lang=fro|goster||to taste}}, from {{etyl|la}} {{term|lang=la|gustus||a tasting}}.

